==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Myopic
<hw>My*op"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to, or
affected with, or characterized by, myopia; nearsighted.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Myopic astigmatism</b></col>, <cd>a condition in which
the eye is affected with myopia in one meridian only.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Myops</ent>⟦br⟧
